Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.40,0:00:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.15,0:00:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,in the Saimori household,\Ndid they all make it out okay after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.70,0:00:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.45,0:00:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.01,0:00:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after what they did,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.97,0:00:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,you're still concerning yourself\Nwith them?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.50,0:00:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I am truly relieved that you're alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.52,0:00:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And then... and the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.63,0:00:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It burned down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.76,0:00:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.97,0:00:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Kudo, I would like to make a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Will you take me\Nto see the Saimori house?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.52,0:00:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I would like to see it one last time.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.33,0:01:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,MY HAPPY MARRIAGE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,EPISODE 7\NMODERN LADY OF SUMMER FLOWERS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.85,0:02:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful! Watch your step.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.81,0:02:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.15,0:02:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's true.\NEverything really did burn down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.80,0:02:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.74,0:03:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Since they lost their home,\NShinichi and Kanoko left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.37,0:03:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They fired most of their servants\Nand moved to their house in the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.79,0:03:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,In essence, the Saimoris are ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.67,0:03:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not entirely their fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tatsuishi family is\Nlikely to blame for this,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,but the public isn't aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.19,0:03:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There won't be any legal prosecution.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.07,0:03:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But regardless,\Nthe head of the family was forced out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.12,0:03:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazushi, the eldest,\Nwill now inherit that title.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.06,0:03:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The new head has accepted restrictions\Nunder my supervision.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tatsuishi family will answer\Nto the Kudos from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.20,0:03:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And... Kaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.66,0:03:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,She has a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll live and work in a household\Nthat is known for its strictness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That place will be good for her.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.27,0:03:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She needs more life experience.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.01,0:04:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaya, can we talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.86,0:04:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'm going to head out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it? Is that going\Nto be enough to bring with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.10,0:04:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that a joke? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaya. This can't change,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.79,0:04:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but we can start over again from here on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I will rebuild the Saimori house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.03,0:04:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not done!\NThis isn't the end for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't act all high and mighty!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.29,0:04:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say you were going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll be on my way then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.65,0:04:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you. Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}My mother planted this cherry blossom tree\Nwhen she married.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.06,0:05:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}This is what you wanted to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.34,0:05:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.52,0:05:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It felt as though my mother was calling me\Nback to this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.13,0:05:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I did this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.31,0:06:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I was reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.98,0:06:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.22,0:06:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I was brazen with my efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.61,0:06:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,My actions were unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.57,0:06:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Kudo, that's just not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Everything you had to do that day\Nwas for greater good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Things had to be that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.02,0:06:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm moving forward. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we get going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.66,0:06:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case,\Nwith the Saimori family so scattered,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.89,0:06:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt we'll be able to hold\Nthe betrothal ceremony with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.25,0:06:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Betrothal?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Regarding our situation together,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.01,0:06:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we might start the proceedings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.09,0:06:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no reason to delay it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.85,0:06:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll most likely end up meeting\Nwith the former head eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.60,0:06:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying that I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.45,0:06:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,m-meet your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.29,0:07:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, as soon as that man hears\Nabout a young lady in her prime,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.29,0:07:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,he brings up marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.79,0:07:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It has always frustrated me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.53,0:07:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I suppose he was the one\Nwho requested this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.88,0:07:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Did he approach my father\Nto make the marriage arrangements?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.09,0:07:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'll make sure\Nthat I'm not a disappointment to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would he think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, um, if he proposed the arrangement,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,he was likely hoping\Nyou would be with Kaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if that may be the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.88,0:07:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I've made my decision\Nso he'd better stay out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.68,0:07:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- Huh?\N- Mm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.49,0:07:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Koji.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kudo, thank you\Nfor all of your help the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How's your recovery going, Miyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.43,0:08:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, thank you for asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.17,0:08:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo, could we have a moment to talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Koji, the other day,\Nthank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I was only capable\Nof calling on Mr. Kudo for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.11,0:08:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Lord Kudo said that he wouldn't\Nhave been able to find me without you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.05,0:08:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,so I might've still been there otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.09,0:08:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, he said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.21,0:08:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}This is the last\NI'll be in town for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Where will you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.34,0:08:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,To the old capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll retrain myself there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My lack of ability has been made\Nvery apparent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to feel powerless anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.47,0:08:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I'm sure...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kaya's going to do her best\Nwhere she'll be working.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.81,0:09:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I'll do my best too.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to become so much stronger
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.21,0:09:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,then I can protect what I want and when.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember\Non that day what I was saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.68,0:09:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.67,0:09:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.38,0:09:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I only ever wanted to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.17,0:09:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Just spend all of our days\Nhappy together like when we were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.24,0:09:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted us to be--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.81,0:09:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what day you're referring to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.20,0:09:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a big deal anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad we got to talk. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I should probably get going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.21,0:10:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo, till next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Alright, time to start over.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.99,0:10:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We started\Nour engagement procedure.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was such an easy task.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.54,0:10:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We simply signed our names.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the end,\Nthere wasn't a betrothal ceremony{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.77,0:10:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}between the two families.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.09,0:10:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There were only\Na few of us in the house, but...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.51,0:10:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...now it was official.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.76,0:10:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once the ink has dried,\Nwe were formally engaged.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,KIYOKA KUDO\NMIYO SAIMORI
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.74,0:11:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!\NThat's the start. Your first step.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The new Madam Kudo! I'm thrilled!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, the Madam? Oh, my goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.99,0:11:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.79,0:11:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,One moment. I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you must be Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.59,0:11:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you. My name is Hazuki Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.43,0:11:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyoka's older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're wanting\Nto re-educate yourself as a lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.49,0:11:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, is that a bad thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't a bad thing for you to want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.21,0:11:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.27,0:11:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I can look for a teacher on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.34,0:11:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stay out of the way\Nand promise not to cause trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.45,0:12:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So I ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't feel the need to bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Your face is bright red.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.22,0:12:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you fighting a fever?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.31,0:12:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, you feel normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel fine. I don't have a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.19,0:12:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.46,0:12:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just, um, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make such a sad face.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.12,0:12:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'll allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.54,0:12:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.31,0:12:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I already have\Nsomeone in mind for a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They can come here.\NI can discuss it with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:12:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's terribly kind of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.23,0:13:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to be so formal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.44,0:13:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just making use of someone\Nwho has lots of time on her hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.31,0:13:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Please have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, great! Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.67,0:13:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I was actually really thirsty\Nso this is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was told you're Lord Kudo's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.95,0:13:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Don't we look alike?\NEspecially in the eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.30,0:13:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone always says\Nthey look like Kiyoka's.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.72,0:13:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's true! Um, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Hazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.73,0:13:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What a joy it is to see you again, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.09,0:13:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Yurie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.55,0:13:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my goodness!\NIt really has been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It truly feels like forever\Nsince we saw each other in a flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.70,0:13:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It is so wonderful to see you doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.10,0:13:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I can say\Nthe same for you, Miss Hazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, you are the same as ever, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.23,0:13:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?\NAren't you supposed to be at work?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.29,0:13:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.54,0:14:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.75,0:14:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so cold that you end up\Nsucking the fun out of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.63,0:14:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you still be like that
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.07,0:14:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,when you have\Nsuch an adorable fiancée like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you leave me alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.39,0:14:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo, let's get to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.93,0:14:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is it alright if I call you Miyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.64,0:14:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright then, Miyo,\NI am going to be your new teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyoka had requested my help\Non your behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.73,0:14:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you told about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.07,0:14:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.19,0:14:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Kiyoka. Did you really not tell her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.01,0:14:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I did tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.03,0:14:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.41,0:14:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyoka's not the best at communicating.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.56,0:14:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt that it'd be going out\Non a limb to assume...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...you didn't tell her about me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.11,0:14:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I... He said...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.53,0:14:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I will take on the responsibility\Nof turning you into a refined young lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much, Miss Hazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.54,0:14:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the season of tree peonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not its only name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.39,0:14:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,In another language,\Nthey're called dahlias.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.75,0:15:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Got a nice ring to it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I love it! This flower's the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo, why don't you join me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.43,0:15:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So do you have\Na favorite flower in this yard?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.69,0:15:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.11,0:15:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not too familiar\Nwith the names of flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that is a weed\Ncalled the dayflower.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.08,0:15:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Does that mean that\Neven different weeds have names?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.56,0:15:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how small the flower,\Nthey all have names.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.10,0:15:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And they are all beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The dayflower is named that\Nbecause it only blooms for one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.09,0:15:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite that, it shoots straight upward\Nwith a bold blue bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.89,0:15:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that they're all lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.77,0:16:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,For the very brief amount of time that\Nany flower enthralls its petals for us,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.75,0:16:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,well, they're always working\Nto be their best.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.86,0:16:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's true with us too, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.15,0:16:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to live as beautifully\Nas we can during our life,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.14,0:16:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,let's do our best to bloom, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ENCOURAGEMENT OF HOMEMAKING
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hop right into it then!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.56,0:16:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A little bird told me you want to learn\Nto carry yourself as a lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.81,0:16:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe it or not,\NI have a wealth of knowledge in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I've taken countless lessons on the topic
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,while I even graduated\Nfrom finishing school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.03,0:16:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm confident\Nin teaching you the basics.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.41,0:16:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take it easy, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.04,0:16:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I just... I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.68,0:17:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really happy you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.06,0:17:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.08,0:17:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This whole experience is an honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.94,0:17:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You are my fiancé's sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.23,0:17:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and I get to have\Nthe privilege of learning from you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.01,0:17:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,to be a refined lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.47,0:17:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh, my goodness!\NYou're such a sweet, wonderful girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.77,0:17:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyoka, how about\NI bring her home with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.94,0:17:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.77,0:17:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a spoilsport!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.58,0:17:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo could learn a lot more\Nif she were with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.75,0:17:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be a far more\Nimmersive environment for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.34,0:17:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I said no.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.76,0:17:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were to take Miyo back home with me,\Nit'd feel empty here,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.95,0:17:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't doubt\Nthat you'd be lonely if it was just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That, that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I think it's best we set a goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a surefire way to internalize\Neverything that you've learned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So set a goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.92,0:17:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.86,0:17:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have a certain goal\Nthat you want to reach,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.69,0:17:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,then working hard towards it is a breeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a party coming up\Nin two months that would be perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.97,0:18:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Both Kiyoka and I were\Nalready invited to attend,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.83,0:18:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,so it would be great\Nif you came with us to feel things out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.90,0:18:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. You don't need\Nto panic at the word "party"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.88,0:18:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,as it's more of a casual get-together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.75,0:18:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But I, I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.92,0:18:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree that you should give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.78,0:18:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Kudo, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.99,0:18:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You can study all you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.87,0:18:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's pointless\Nif you can't put it to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.00,0:18:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I can understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I will join you for this party.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise there's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.09,0:18:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you aren't going to be thrown out\Nin a dress and told to go dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll know the basics like the back\Nof your hand in no time, Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.95,0:18:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So just go and enjoy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.93,0:18:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, you think I will?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.66,0:18:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. I'll make\Na schedule for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.02,0:18:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,By the next time we meet,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.21,0:18:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have it all put together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.65,0:18:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's do our best
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.54,0:18:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.74,0:18:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miss Hazuki is so generous.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.62,0:19:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's such a lovely lady.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.12,0:19:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hope I can be like her one day.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to be a wife\Nwho is good for Lord Kudo.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.26,0:19:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A gift-user's nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.39,0:19:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo. I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.44,0:19:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, stop! Please stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.70,0:19:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're alright. You're okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.92,0:19:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Another nightmare.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.17,0:19:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the same kind of ability as before.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.09,0:19:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no sign of a break\Nin the barrier around the house.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.51,0:20:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's highly unlikely\Nthat an intruder could get in.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's only one avenue left...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.56,0:20:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Usuba...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.93,0:20:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Put up the barrier again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.74,0:20:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Focus all of your senses!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.47,0:21:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,General Okaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.47,0:21:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry that I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.39,0:21:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize\Nfor interrupting your work, Kiyoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.85,0:21:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told His Majesty had a revelation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.69,0:21:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be heading there soon\Nto report about the Tatsuishi incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.94,0:21:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like you to join.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.45,0:21:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, there was another matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Something I wanted to tell you\Nbefore we head into this meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.51,0:21:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.29,0:21:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The Grave has been hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.29,0:21:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.46,0:21:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we don't know too much yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.46,0:21:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}but they unsealed The Grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.22,0:22:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The time has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.60,0:22:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm coming to get you, Miyo.
